  "instructions": [
    "Mix together chickpeas, chopped cilantro, chopped onion, chopped garlic, ground cumin, ground coriander, cayenne pepper, salt, and lemon juice.",
    "Heat a tablespoon of olive oil in a pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Shape chickpea mixture into small patties.",
    "Add patties to the pan and cook until golden brown on both sides.",
    "Transfer patties to a pressure cooker.",
    "Add enough water to cover the patties and pressure cook at 115c for 10 minutes.",
